claim.claim-text:
1. A clear aqueous microemulsion pesticidal formulation consisting essentially of, as active ingredients
(a) a saccharide, esterified to at least one monounsaturated C16-C20 fatty acid to form a complex;
(b) an anionic surfactant blend;
(c) nonionic and/or amphiphilic surfactant blend that promotes microemulsion formation; and
(d) wherein said clear aqueous formulation has a turbidity of less than 3 NTU.
